Package com.composum.sling.dashboard.service

Interface ResourceExtractService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DashboardExtractService
    public interface ResourceExtractService
    a service to extract resources together with all referenced resources mapped to a set of target resources (target paths) with all references adjusted to the target paths

                                                              boolean dryRun,

                                                              @NotNull ResourceExtractService.ExtractSession session)
        creates an extractor to copy source resources to the mapping target paths in the same repository with reference adjustment
        Parameters:
        config - the configuration to use, 'null': the default configuration of the service is used
        mode - the mode to control how properties copy to existing target resources are handled
        dryRun - if 'true' nothing is persistent changed, the affected paths are logged
        session - the extract session to control the execution
        Returns:
        the copy extractor

        creates an extractor to extract the source resources into a ZIP file of XML sourcecode entries with or without mapping to the target paths and with reference adjustment if paths are mapped
        Parameters:
        config - the configuration to use, 'null': the default configuration of the service is used
        targetFilter - an additional filter to specify the content of interest that should be stored in the ZIP
        mapToTarget - if 'false' the sources are not mapped to the configured target paths
        session - the extract session to control the execution
        outputStream - the output stream to store the generated ZIP file
        Returns:
        the zip extractor

        Parameters:
        config - the configuration to use, 'null': the default configuration of the service is used
